title: GetBlock - Ethhub

# GetBlock

## About

GetBlock is a Blockchain-as-a-Service (BaaS) platform that provides a fast and easy API connection to full nodes from many leading blockchain platforms. It allows you to request on-chain information from a node without the need to set up one manually with JSON-RPC, REST, and WebSockets.
GetBlock provides access to the Ethereum (ETH) node with JSON-RPC and WebSockets. Available clients: OpenEthereum(Parity), Hyperledger Besu.


### Main products & Documentation:

* [GetBlock](https://getblock.io)
* [GetBlock API key](https://getblock.io/#access)
* [Documentation](https://getblock.io/docs/get-started/authentication-with-api-key)


